{"id":"errors/NG02800","title":"NG02800: HttpClient 配置中缺少 JSONP 支持。","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng02800-missing-jsonp-support-in-httpclient-configuration\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"biywt55hrqvc2lu1tvta1ne9z\">NG02800: HttpClient 配置中缺少 JSONP 支持。<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG02800#ng02800-missing-jsonp-support-in-httpclient-configuration\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  \n  \n\n  <div class=\"error-description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG02800#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"as5g4bsad4oq65i418kx8iint\">当你尝试发起 <code>JSONP</code> 请求却没有在 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClient</a></code> 配置中提供必要的支持时，Angular 就会抛出此错误。要启用 <code>JSONP</code> 支持，你可以执行以下操作之一：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"87mrd7ek3nydkqa78kh2aqehm\">当使用 <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a></code> 时，在 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideHttpClient</a></code> 函数调用期间添加 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/withJsonpSupport\" class=\"code-anchor\">withJsonpSupport</a>()</code> 作为参数（例如 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideHttpClient</a>(<a href=\"api/common/http/withJsonpSupport\" class=\"code-anchor\">withJsonpSupport</a>())</code> ）</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5v4vwskecnvo9yd026sisoyfn\">当使用基于 NgModule 的引导程序时，在根 AppModule 中导入 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClientJsonpModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClientJsonpModule</a></code>。</li>\n</ul>\n\n  </div>\n\n\n  \n  <br>\n\n  <div class=\"debugging\">\n    <h2 id=\"debugging-the-error\">如何排除本错误<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG02800#debugging-the-error\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6vbh7fvpp25bcor1gc849alrk\">通过在使用 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/provideHttpClient\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideHttpClient</a>()</code> 时调用 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/withJsonpSupport\" class=\"code-anchor\">withJsonpSupport</a>()</code> 函数或如前所述导入 <code><a href=\"api/common/http/HttpClientJsonpModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">HttpClientJsonpModule</a></code> 模块，确保将 JSONP 支持添加到了你的应用程序中。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e66n3pq8t755na9ikrkcm2l5g\">有关详细信息，请参阅<a href=\"/guide/http-make-jsonp-request\">发出 JSONP 请求</a>。</p>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  </div>\n  \n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - errors\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /guide/http-make-jsonp-request\n - api/common/http/HttpClient\n - api/common/http/HttpClientJsonpModule\n - api/common/http/provideHttpClient\n - api/common/http/withJsonpSupport\n - api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\n - errors/NG02800#debugging-the-error\n - errors/NG02800#description\n - errors/NG02800#ng02800-missing-jsonp-support-in-httpclient-configuration\n-->"}